{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"1877","airdate":"1488999600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Bozzy and the Bint","showname":"BBKB","blurb":"It's the Taint of the Week\u2122 again, so it's time for Boz to utter complete bollocks in between your requests. Thankfully, Kate is here to translate some of it into English. All aboard the Train-Wreck, WOO WOOH!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Bozzy and the Bint<\/big><\/strong><br \/>BBKB","nice_airdate":"Wednesday 8th March, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1876","airdate":"1489086000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"The Uncracked Tracks","blurb":"Well ,last weeks show went really well soundwise, so let's go full force. Taking on your Commodore requests as usual and playing the occasional weird ones as well. Tune in and most importantly have fun =)","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>The Uncracked Tracks","nice_airdate":"Thursday 9th March, 2017<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1878","airdate":"1489309200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PMPVsYouTube","blurb":"We've had PMPVsYouTubeCareers, but this time the topic is YouTube itself for a bit. The venture into the visual domain has not been without a few obstacles along the way. There's been a bit of Content ID'ing and some integration hassle. Given that the visual portion of the show is not going away any time soon, it seems like an appropriate thing to talk about at this juncture.\n\nSo let's take a trip together, back into the the past, some of the present, and perhaps even the future. I promise there'll be some delicious C-64 along the way!\n\nSee ya'll there!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PMPVsYouTube","nice_airdate":"Sunday 12th March, 2017<br \/>at 10:00 USRT"}]}